# Cloudflare Pages — https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

# 静态构建产物（CSS/JS/图片/OG 图）：文件名含 hash，长期缓存
/_astro/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/og/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable